column7: #sad on reddit. Not happy. Very melancholy but comfortable.
Shame at lack of self discipline - feel like a loser
#tense #happy #fulfilled fantasizing about a wonderful, cool bohemian, grand life in London
Doesn't last too long. On reddit all night
Spoke to Joel. Ordered pizza. I have a desire to get out of this now, an awareness of the good things of life. Women and people become attractive again.
#average this is the best I am able to feel. Reasonably bright vas happy but still with that bit of tension, unease, threat and badness
Got our of this one: hot fed up, blocked the internet
#angry fed up with being on the beach
Was thinking about career, very optimistic. Excited about job prospects
